azureWebPubSub.common.description: An Azure Web PubSub extension for Visual Studio Code.
azureWebPubSub.enableOutputTimestamps: Prepends each line displayed in the output channel with a timestamp.
azureWebPubSub.service.createInPortal: Create Web PubSub Service in Portal
azureWebPubSub.service.createInPortal.in: Create Web PubSub Service in Azure Portal.
azureWebPubSub.deleteConfirmation: The behavior to use when confirming delete of a Azure Web PubSub.
azureWebPubSub.deleteConfirmation.EnterN: Prompts with an input box where you enter the Azure Web PubSub name to delete.
azureWebPubSub.deleteConfirmation.ClickB: Prompts with a warning dialog where you click a button to delete.
